    "updated_at": "2015-05-22T11:21:42Z",
    "body": "true, your app crashes because electron makes several packages available in the renderer process. For example the `require` method is also available in the renderer process. If any of your logic looks for the `require` method and uses this as indicator if the app is running in node or not... this may cause the issue.\n\nTo answer your other question, check the docs at https://github.com/atom/electron/blob/master/docs/api/remote.md here it's fully documented how to get started with remoting in electron\n"
